ws, app stores, business listings, and more. It supports use cases across digital marketing, AI development, ecommerce, and enterprise applications.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"eaf10762-f7eb-4b0f-ac18-2cd00a51579e\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 558.56\n}\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"mellow-mist","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"news heat score trending\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"x_developer.2.trends.by.woeid.retrieve.v2.21f95686\",\n      \"name\": \"Get Trends by WOEID\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieves trending topics for a specific location identified by its WOEID.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"woeid\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The WOEID of the place to lookup a trend for.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"max_trends\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The maximum number of results.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"trend.fields\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A comma separated list of Trend fields to display.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"woeid\": 1\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Use X API to fetch posts, users, trends, etc.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 744.33,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.302\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Topics Tracker\",\n      \"description\": \"Track and aggregate hot topics from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter platform. Supports multiple domains: AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"List of domains to query. Available: AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science. If not specified, queries all domains.\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域列表。可选：AI、Finance、Crypto、Tech、Science。如不指定则查询所有领域。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return per domain\",\n            \"zh\": \"每个领域返回结果的最大数量\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"min_engagement\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Minimum engagement (likes + retweets + replies) for filtering posts\",\n            \"zh\": \"用于过滤的最小互动量（点赞+转发+回复）\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Events Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Summarize today's hot events on X/Twitter for a domain: fetch new posts then use LLM to summarize events and return event list with post ids.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domain(s) to summarize\",\n            \"zh\": \"要总结的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_account_hottest_post_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Account Hottest Post (7 Days)\",\n      \"description\": \"Return the single hottest post (by engagement) from a given X/Twitter account in the last 7 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"username\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"X/Twitter username (without @)\",\n            \"zh\": \"X账号用户名（不含@）\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"account\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Alias for username\",\n            \"zh\": \"同 username\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_account_hottest_post_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain New Posts Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Search today's new posts from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter with full fields: text, images, media, metrics. Supports AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domains to query\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": null\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"coingecko.search.trending.retrieve.v3.548c6bf0\",\n      \"name\": \"Trending Search List\",\n      \"description\": \"This endpoint allows you **query trending search coins, NFTs and categories on CoinGecko in the last 24 hours**\",\n      \"provider_description\": \"CoinGecko API provides onchain DEX data across 250+ blockchain networks, 1,700+ decentralized exchanges (DEXes), and 15M+ tokens, powered by GeckoTerminal. It offers price feeds, market data, metadata, and historical data of crypto assets, NFTs, and exchanges. Includes WebSocket API for real-time data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.tonechart.retrieve.v2.a7b24341\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Tone Chart\",\n      \"description\": \"Generates a histogram showing the distribution of article tones (from extremely negative to extremely positive) for articles mentioning a specific query over the last 3 months.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query phrase\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API operation mode\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"tonechart\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"tonechart\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 19242.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.077\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"dataforseo.keywords_data.google_trends.explore.live.create.v3.07aba022\",\n      \"name\": \"Setting Live ‘Google Trends Explore’ Tasks\",\n      \"description\": \"This endpoint will provide you with the keyword popularity data from the ‘Explore’ feature of Google Trends. You can check keyword trends for Google Search, Google News, Google Images, Google Shopping, and YouTube.\",\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"device\": \"desktop\",\n          \"date_to\": \"2024-12-31\",\n          \"keywords\": [\n            \"example keyword\"\n          ],\n          \"date_from\": \"2024-01-01\",\n          \"category_code\": 0,\n          \"location_name\": \"United States\",\n          \"time_offset_unit\": \"week\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"DataForSEO provides a comprehensive suite of APIs for SEO, keyword research, SERP data, backlinks, reviews, app stores, business listings, and more. It supports use cases across digital marketing, AI development, ecommerce, and enterprise applications.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"dataforseo.keywords_data.google_trends.explore.task_post.create.v3.edeec36e\",\n      \"name\": \"Setting ‘Google Trends Explore’ Tasks\",\n      \"description\": \"This endpoint will provide you with the keyword popularity data from the ‘Explore’ feature of Google Trends. You can check keyword trends for Google Search, Google News, Google Images, Google Shopping, and YouTube.\",\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"geo\": \"US\",\n          \"date_to\": \"2023-12-31\",\n          \"keywords\": [\n            \"iphone\",\n            \"samsung\"\n          ],\n          \"date_from\": \"2023-01-01\",\n          \"category_code\": 0,\n          \"time_offset_unit\": \"week\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"DataForSEO provides a comprehensive suite of APIs for SEO, keyword research, SERP data, backlinks, reviews, app stores, business listings, and more. It supports use cases across digital marketing, AI development, ecommerce, and enterprise applications.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"dataforseo.trends.merged_data.retrieve.v3.8271644c\",\n      \"name\": \"DataForSEO Trends API - Merged Data Endpoint\",\n      \"description\": \"Combines data from Explore, Subregion Interests, and Demography endpoints to provide a comprehensive view of search interest trends.\",\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"keywords\": [\n            \"bitcoin\",\n            \"ethereum\"\n          ]\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"DataForSEO provides a comprehensive suite of APIs for SEO, keyword research, SERP data, backlinks, reviews, app stores, business listings, and more. It supports use cases across digital marketing, AI development, ecommerce, and enterprise applications.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"eaf10762-f7eb-4b0f-ac18-2cd00a51579e\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 558.56\n}\n","name":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772518191844}}
